title: Product Feature: FoodSaver® 2-in-1 Vacuum Sealing System
description: Learn about the versatility and convenience of the FoodSaver 2-in-1 Vacuum Sealing System.

asset.author: FoodSaver
asset.description: Learn about the versatility and convenience of the FoodSaver® 2-in-1 Vacuum Sealing System. Learn more: http://www.foodsaver.com/vacuum-sealers/the-foodsaver-v4865-2-in-1-vacuum-sealing-system/FSFSSL4865-DTC.html#start=1

transcripts: Introducing the FoodSaver 2-in-1 Vacuum Sealing System. This innovative sealing solution now gives you more ways to seal and more ways to save. The FoodSaver Vacuum Sealing System keeps food fresh up to five times longer and helps you save up to $2700 a year. The FoodSaver Vacuum Sealing System automatically senses the FoodSaver bag and starts the vacuum sealing process then applies a virtually airtight heat seal to help prevent freezer burn and spoilage. Why throw away expensive meat and fish when you can save it with a FoodSaver System? The retractable handheld sealer works with zipper bags, containers and accessories for fridge and pantry items, perfect for deli meats and cheeses, cereal, snacks and more. Unlike other vacuum sealers, the FoodSave Vacuum Sealer comes with a pull out draw and patented removable drip tray, making clean up a breeze and extending the life of your appliance. Keep your food fresh up to five times longer with the FoodSaver 2-in-1 Vacuum Sealing System. More ways to seal, more ways to save.
